Just a collection of skills I’ve picked up through building products, working with AI, and solving problems.

Nothing fancy. Just things I know how to do, that I have put into skills for AI agents.

Mostly focused on startups, product development, technical leadership, AI, and making good decisions with limited time and information.

---

## Mine skills

| Skill | Hvad den gør |
|-------|--------------|
| [product-concept-architect](product-concept-architect/) | Strategisk sparringspartner til produktbeslutninger — giver konkrete retninger og reel pushback |
| [product-naming-parallel](product-naming-parallel/) | Spawner 11 navngivningsøvelser parallelt og filtrerer til de 3 stærkeste kandidater |
| [product-naming-v2](product-naming-v2/) | Struktureret hjælp til at navngive produkter, tjenester eller virksomheder |
| [ruthless-startup-cto-advisor](ruthless-startup-cto-advisor/) | Nådesløs startup CTO-rådgiver — griller dig ét spørgsmål ad gangen som djævelens advokat |

