## Eksterne skills

| Skill | Hvad den gør | Install |
|-------|--------------|---------|
| [cto-team](https://github.com/alirezarezvani/claude-cto-team) | Strategisk CTO-team med agenter til arkitektur, planvalidering og teknologibeslutninger — kommandoer: `/cto` `/validate` `/design` `/decide` | `claude plugins marketplace add https://github.com/alirezarezvani/claude-cto-team` → `claude plugins install alirezarezvani/claude-cto-team` |
| [superpowers](https://github.com/obra/superpowers) | Strukturerede workflows til kodning: TDD, debugging, planning, code review, parallelle agenter og branch-afslutning | `claude plugins install superpowers` |
| [academic-research-skills](https://github.com/Imbad0202/academic-research-skills) | Komplet akademisk research-pipeline: research, paperskrivning, peer review, revision og finalisering — kommandoer: `/ars-full` `/ars-reviewer` `/ars-lit-review` `/ars-citation-check` | `claude plugins marketplace add https://github.com/Imbad0202/academic-research-skills` → `claude plugins install academic-research-skills` |

