## UX

| Skill | Hvad den gør | Kilde / Install |
|-------|--------------|-----------------|
| [frontend-design](https://claude.com/plugins/frontend-design) | Design-guide til produktion-grade frontends med distinkt æstetik — vælger en klar retning (brutalist, editorial, luxury osv.) og undgår generisk AI-slop | Officielt Claude-plugin: `claude plugins install frontend-design` |
| [awesome-ux-skills](https://github.com/Graunephar/awesome-ux-skills) *(forket fra [tommyjepsen/awesome-ux-skills](https://github.com/tommyjepsen/awesome-ux-skills))* | 19 UX-skills: empathy mapping, journey mapping, personas, heuristikker, ux-research, persuasive UX m.m. | `git clone git@github.com:Graunephar/awesome-ux-skills.git && bash awesome-ux-skills/install.sh` |